            "description": "<div id=\"newsBody\">\n<span class=\"newsDetail\" style=\"font-size: 13px; font-family:MingLiu;Arial;\">&lt;汇港通讯&gt;      欧洲股市早段上升。英国富时100指数报10,169.72点，升32.37点(0.32%)；德国DAX指数报25,436.33点，升15.67点(0.06%)；法国CAC 40指数报8,384.92点，升37.72点(0.45%)。  (WL)</span>\n</div>",
